code: /**  * @return true if the first parameter is LT/LTEQ/EQ/GTEQ/GT the second  */ boolean matches(BigInteger first, BigInteger second).
@Override public boolean matches(BigInteger first, BigInteger second) {     return first.compareTo(second) < 0. }
@Override public boolean matches(BigInteger first, BigInteger second) {     return first.compareTo(second) <= 0. }
